{"tid":1070992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲富豪請私人助理年薪30萬包食住　26歲型男：陪我環遊世界","createTime":"2019-03-21T04:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T00:33:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":298,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"4d3247d75152e17874ee316e402190604404de57","tid":1070992,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:48:57.000Z","msg":"想要一份「筍工」嗎？現在可能是機會。澳洲一名26歲富豪白手興家，為了擴展他一手經營的電子商務生意，他現時公開招騁私人助理，年薪2.8萬英鎊 （約29萬港元）。這名型男富豪希望助理能陪他環遊世界，更能提供住宿和伙食補助，而職責上包括到世界各地進行研討會和演說、安排國內外旅遊行程等，需要高強的組織能力和積極的工作態度。<br />\n據外國媒體報道，26歲富豪Matthew Lepre來自澳洲，靠創辦電子商務生意賺錢，而他現時公開招聘私人助理，年薪約29萬港元。由於工作關係，私人助理必須和他走訪世界各地不同公司開會和演說，其中以美國、日本和杜拜為最常去的地方，出國食宿費會由他支付，更會給予員工健康保險。而他強調，這位私人助理必須要陪他環遊世界：<br />\n&quot;歡迎大家和我一起冒險，探索新世界！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n他表示29萬港元只是底薪，如應徵者表現能幹，薪金可再上調。他希望能請到一名能幹的助理，有關求職條件如下：<br />\n安排旅遊行程<br />\n擁有豐富的電腦技術<br />\n熟悉各種社交網絡媒體<br />\n高強組織能力<br />\n注重細節<br />\n工作態度積極<br />\n守時<br />\nMatthew Lepre本身家境貧窮，幼時隨母親移民澳洲，依靠著救世軍贈送的食物過活。以往曾就讀牙醫課程，但他卻選擇輟學賺錢，曾試過一天打3份工，後來掌握了網上業務知識，開始自己的電子商務生意，創辦網上商店，主攻男女美容產品，並在創業兩年後，每月賺大約30多萬港元，更曾在2017年美國AM2 Better Your Best創業大賽勝出。他喜歡一邊工作，一邊旅遊，尋找理想生活，亦想與人分享美好的人生經驗，體驗理想人生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2300000/2302990/millionaire_thumb_20190321_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2300000%2F2302990%2Fmillionaire_thumb_20190321_ch_1024.jpg&h=968c5d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2300000/2302990/02_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2300000%2F2302990%2F02_1024.jpg&h=d243343e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2300000/2302990/04_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2300000%2F2302990%2F04_1024.jpg&h=72a6ebe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2300000/2302990/11_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2300000%2F2302990%2F11_1024.jpg&h=f286b986&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"972f04c4658d5574792163f25abd59cc8a73fa95","tid":1070992,"uid":108467,"like":608,"dislike":9,"score":599,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:50:17.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8207de58d873206b728df70cf0f8a27731f9c4","tid":1070992,"uid":14548,"like":830,"dislike":7,"score":823,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:51:26.000Z","msg":"以為月薪，都係岀返去"},{"pid":"4d5c667d63499a50c03c725d989b4474b15d164c","tid":1070992,"uid":33907,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"即刻去應徵先"},{"pid":"11084110ad10ed4d5cc3ff687d1c43877bbc3861","tid":1070992,"uid":113626,"like":141,"dislike":5,"score":136,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:52:58.000Z","msg":"港男成個ladyboy咁岩哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94060f40f45c6e6737fe05131da36fdb9aa9203","tid":1070992,"uid":185126,"like":270,"dislike":4,"score":266,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:53:12.000Z","msg":"Gay真係有樣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7dbe698bf4c40aa116b8f6673e14ffccfd9dfca","tid":1070992,"uid":61207,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:53:59.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f59cacb0d1c75ac81f0135273eb096c67597a3e","tid":1070992,"uid":26770,"like":9,"dislike":11,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:54:32.000Z","msg":"另一條友應該係公司的PARNER果類<br />\n應該係IN女炮友"},{"pid":"a329a5e025bbdf95f486410d8d836b5dbd965f9c","tid":1070992,"uid":46910,"like":323,"dislike":32,"score":2